caption: When a talented photographer friend comes to visit, you let her put you in front of the camera (even though you’ve been avoiding it for years - easy to do since leaving NYC for a west coast town where I can go weeks talking only to my animals). @emmakmorris is such a joy of a human and an amazing photographer, and I’m so happy to have met her by chance 10 years ago. Thank you for capturing Mazie and I in the studio, Emma!
